{"tid":1607843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平稱沒有任何力量可撼動祖國地位","createTime":"2019-10-01T04:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T05:50:29.000Z","uid":56881,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"704fe1462315c203c54c410130a148640e9753b7","tid":1607843,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%A8%B1%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%AF%E6%92%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%A5%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-021955602.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2592%25BC%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D-021955602.html&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CddUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=a8ba664d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%A8%B1%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%AF%E6%92%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%A5%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-021955602.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今日是國慶70周年，北京今早舉行慶祝大會。國家主席習近平在天安門城樓發表講話時表示，70年前的今天，毛澤東向世界宣告中華人民共和國成立，中國人民從此站起來，改變了近代以後100多年，中國積貧積弱、受人欺凌的悲慘命運。<br />\n<br />\n習近平說，過去70年來，全國各族人民，同心同德，艱苦奮鬥，取得刮目相看的成就，屹立東方，沒有任何力量能夠撼動祖國地位，沒有任何力量能夠阻止中國人及中華民族的前進步伐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />oh rely?"},{"pid":"24be488ed99581dd204fa9e9e65770938be95c8b","tid":1607843,"uid":74155,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"flag已立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c848e9ecdac16fa82fbe0f8d21ccdb9e34bf8528","tid":1607843,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ff